<p>
  The Entra (Azure AD) client secret for the reimbursements mailbox app expires on
  <strong><%= @expires_on.to_fs(:rfc822) %></strong>, <%= @days_left %> days from now.
</p>
<p>
  When it expires, receipt emails to the reimbursements mailbox stop being processed
  and replies stop being sent.
</p>
<p>To rotate it:</p>
<ol>
  <li>entra.microsoft.com → App registrations → "BlackLightning Reimbursements Mailbox" → Certificates &amp; secrets → New client secret.</li>
  <li>Update <code>azure_client_secret</code> (and <code>azure_secret_expires_on</code>) in the Rails production credentials, and the fnox/Bitwarden entry for development.</li>
  <li>Redeploy.</li>
</ol>
<p>This warning repeats daily until the recorded expiry date is updated.</p>
